<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>🎨 La Regla de los 10 Minutos — Libro Mágico para Colorear</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@500;700;800;900&family=Chewy&family=Nunito:wght@600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   ROOT & RESET
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
:root{
  --ink:#1A1208; --cream:#FFFEF9; --warm:#FFF8ED;
  --brown:#6B3F1A; --amber:#E8890C; --gold:#F5C842;
  --blush:#FFD6E0; --sage:#A8D5A2; --sky:#A8D8F0;
  --lavender:#C9B8F0; --peach:#FFB877;
  --r:24px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
html,body{
  width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #3D1C08 0%, #1A0A03 100%);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   BOOK SHELL — looks like a real children's book
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.book{
  width:min(430px,100vw);
  height:min(660px,100vh);
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  border-radius:4px 20px 20px 4px;
  box-shadow:
    -8px 0 0 #3D1C08,
    -14px 0 0 #5C2D0A,
    -18px 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.6),
    8px 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.6),
    inset -4px 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}
/* spine strip */
.book::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:0;width:14px;height:100%;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,#3D1C08,#6B3F1A);
  z-index:200;border-radius:4px 0 0 4px;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   PAGES
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.page{
  position:absolute;inset:0;left:14px;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  background:var(--cream);
  opacity:0;pointer-events:none;
  transform:translateX(110%) rotateY(-8deg);
  transform-origin:left center;
  transition:transform .5s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1),opacity .4s;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.page.active{opacity:1;pointer-events:all;transform:translateX(0) rotateY(0);}
.page.gone{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-110%) rotateY(8deg);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   NAV BAR
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.nav{
  position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:52px;
  background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(255,253,245,1),rgba(255,253,245,.8));
  border-top:1.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.07);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:0 14px;z-index:80;
}
.nbtn{
  border:none;border-radius:50px;padding:8px 16px;
  font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;
  cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;color:#fff;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;
}
.nbtn:active{transform:scale(.92);}
.nbtn-back{background:#BDB0A0;color:var(--ink);}
.nbtn-next{background:var(--amber);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(232,137,12,.4);}
.nbtn-special{background:var(--brown);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(107,63,26,.4);}
.nbtn:disabled{opacity:.2;cursor:default;transform:none!important;}
.pg-dots{display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center;}
.dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);transition:all .3s;}
.dot.on{background:var(--amber);width:14px;border-radius:3px;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   PAPER TEXTURE overlays
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.paper-texture{
  position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:1;
  background-image:
    repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 27px,rgba(0,0,0,.025) 28px),
    url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='200' height='200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.65' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='200' height='200' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   ── PAGE 0: COVER ──
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
#p0{
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, #FFE0A3 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 80%, #FFB6C1 0%, transparent 50%),
    linear-gradient(160deg,#FFF4D6 0%,#FFE4B0 40%,#FFD0A0 70%,#FFC890 100%);
}
.cover-wrap{
  flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  gap:10px;padding:24px 20px 58px;text-align:center;z-index:2;
}
.cover-ribbon{
  background:var(--brown);color:#fff;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;
  letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:5px 20px;
  border-radius:50px;box-shadow:0 3px 10px rgba(107,63,26,.3);
}
.cover-animals-row{
  display:flex;gap:4px;justify-content:center;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.15));
}
.cov-a{
  font-size:36px;display:inline-block;
  animation:wa 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.cov-a:nth-child(1){animation-delay:.0s;}
.cov-a:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.2s;}
.cov-a:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.4s;}
.cov-a:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.6s;}
.cov-a:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.8s;}
@keyframes wa{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(-3deg);}50%{transform:translateY(-8px) rotate(3deg);}}
.cover-title{
  font-family:'Chewy',cursive;font-size:42px;
  color:var(--brown);text-shadow:3px 3px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.6);
  line-height:1;letter-spacing:.5px;
}
.cover-sub{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',cursive;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;
  color:rgba(107,63,26,.8);line-height:1.3;
}
.cover-pill{
  background:var(--brown);color:var(--gold);
  font-weight:900;font-size:12px;padding:8px 22px;border-radius:50px;
  box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(107,63,26,.25);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
}
.cover-promise{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.65);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
  border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.8);border-radius:16px;
  padding:10px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;
  color:rgba(107,63,26,.85);line-height:1.5;max-width:310px;
}
.cover-promise strong{color:var(--amber);}
.cover-mama{
  font-size:52px;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.15));
  animation:mama-float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes mama-float{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);}50%{transform:translateY(-8px);}}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   ── STANDARD TEXT PAGES ──
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.txt-page{background:var(--cream);}
.txt-body{
  flex:1;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  gap:11px;padding:18px 18px 58px;z-index:2;
}
.pg-label{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
  background:var(--brown);color:var(--gold);
  font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:4px 14px;border-radius:50px;align-self:flex-start;
}
.pg-h1{
  font-family:'Baloo 2',cursive;font-size:22px;font-weight:900;
  color:var(--ink);line-height:1.1;
}
.pg-h1 em{color:var(--amber);font-style:normal;}
.body-p{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#555;line-height:1.65;}
.body-p strong{color:var(--brown);}
.card{
  background:var(--warm);border-radius:14px;padding:10px 13px;
  display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;
  border-left:4px solid var(--amber);
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
}
.card-icon{font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.card-t{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);}
.card-s{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#888;margin-top:2px;}
.tip-box{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFF3DC,#FFE8B5);
  border-radius:14px;padding:11px 14px;
  border-left:4px solid var(--gold);
  font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#6B4A00;line-height:1.55;
}
.tip-box strong{color:var(--brown);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   ── INDEX PAGE ──
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.idx-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;}
.idx-item{
  background:var(--warm);border-radius:12px;padding:9px 13px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;
  border-left:4px solid var(--peach);cursor:pointer;
  transition:transform .15s;
}
.idx-item:active{transform:translateX(5px);}
.idx-e{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;}
.idx-t{font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);flex:1;}
.idx-pg{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#C0A880;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   ── TIMER PAGE ──
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.timer-card{
  background:var(--brown);border-radius:20px;padding:18px;
  text-align:center;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(107,63,26,.35);
}
.timer-n{
  font-family:'Chewy',cursive;font-size:70px;color:var(--gold);
  line-height:1;text-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(245,200,66,.4);
  letter-spacing:2px;
}
.timer-l{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;}
.t-btn{
  background:var(--gold);color:var(--brown);border:none;border-radius:50px;
  padding:10px 28px;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:900;
  cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(245,200,66,.4);transition:all .2s;
}
.t-btn:active{transform:scale(.94);}
.age-guide{
  display:flex;gap:6px;
}
.age-pill{
  flex:1;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
  border-radius:10px;padding:7px 4px;text-align:center;
  font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);line-height:1.4;
}
.age-pill strong{color:var(--gold);font-size:13px;display:block;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   ── COLORING PAGES ──
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.color-page{background:var(--cream);}
.color-layout{
  flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  padding:10px 12px 56px;gap:7px;z-index:2;overflow:hidden;
}
.animal-hdr{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;}
.a-badge{
  background:var(--brown);color:var(--gold);
  width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-weight:900;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0;
}
.a-name{font-family:'Baloo 2',cursive;font-size:20px;font-weight:900;color:var(--ink);}
.a-lesson{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--warm),#FFE8B5);
  border-radius:8px;padding:4px 11px;
  font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--brown);
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;
  border:1.5px solid rgba(232,137,12,.2);
}

/* SVG drawing area */
.drawing-area{
  flex:1;min-height:0;
  background:#fff;border-radius:16px;
  border:2px dashed rgba(0,0,0,.1);
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  box-shadow:inset 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
}
.drawing-area svg{width:100%;height:100%;max-height:240px;}

/* Colour palette */
.palette{
  display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:nowrap;
  overflow-x:auto;padding:2px 0;
}
.palette::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
.swatch{
  width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;
  border:3px solid transparent;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;
  box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
}
.swatch.on{border-color:var(--ink);transform:scale(1.22);}
.swatch:active{transform:scale(.88);}

.tools{display:flex;gap:7px;justify-content:center;}
.tool{
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.06);border:none;border-radius:10px;
  padding:6px 13px;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;
  font-size:12px;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .18s;color:var(--ink);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;
}
.tool:active{transform:scale(.93);}
.tool.er{background:rgba(232,137,12,.12);color:var(--amber);}

.fact{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFF8E6,#FFF3D0);
  border-left:4px solid var(--gold);border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;
  padding:7px 11px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#7A5500;line-height:1.45;
}
.fact strong{color:var(--brown);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   ── ROUTINE / DIPLOMA / FINAL ──
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.time-row{
  background:#fff;border-radius:13px;padding:10px 13px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;
  box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
}
.time-tag{
  border-radius:9px;padding:6px 9px;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;
  color:#fff;min-width:52px;text-align:center;line-height:1.3;flex-shrink:0;
}
.morn{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFB347,#FF8C00);}
.noon{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#52C87A,#2ECC71);}
.nght{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6B8EFF,#4568DC);}
.time-items{flex:1;}
.ti{font-size:12px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);padding:1px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;}

.dip-frame{
  background:linear-gradient(160deg,#FFFBEF,#FFF5D0);
  border:3px solid var(--gold);border-radius:18px;
  padding:16px 18px;text-align:center;position:relative;
  box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1.5px rgba(245,200,66,.3), 0 6px 20px rgba(232,137,12,.15);
}
.dip-frame::before{
  content:'✦ ✦ ✦';position:absolute;top:-13px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  background:var(--cream);padding:0 8px;color:var(--gold);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:5px;
}
.dip-top{font-size:9px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C0A000;}
.dip-main{font-family:'Chewy',cursive;font-size:24px;color:var(--brown);margin:4px 0;}
.dip-sub{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#888;margin-bottom:8px;}
.dip-in{
  border:2px dashed var(--gold);background:rgba(245,200,66,.08);
  border-radius:8px;padding:6px;width:100%;
  font-family:'Chewy',cursive;font-size:20px;color:var(--brown);
  text-align:center;outline:none;margin-bottom:6px;
}
.dip-in::placeholder{color:#D4C080;font-size:14px;}
.dip-animals-row{font-size:24px;letter-spacing:3px;margin:3px 0;}
.dip-footer{font-size:9px;color:#C0A880;border-top:1px solid #EEE;padding-top:6px;margin-top:4px;line-height:1.5;}

/* FINAL page */
#p13{
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 30%,#FFE0A3 0%,transparent 60%),
             linear-gradient(160deg,#FFF4D6 0%,#FFDFA0 60%,#FFD080 100%);
}
.final-wrap{
  flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  gap:13px;padding:28px 22px 58px;text-align:center;z-index:2;
}
.final-big{font-family:'Chewy',cursive;font-size:38px;color:var(--brown);text-shadow:2px 2px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.6);}
.final-sub{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(107,63,26,.8);line-height:1.55;max-width:320px;}
.final-box{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.6);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
  border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.8);border-radius:14px;
  padding:12px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;
  color:rgba(107,63,26,.85);line-height:1.55;width:100%;max-width:330px;
}
.final-box strong{color:var(--amber);}
.restart{
  background:var(--brown);color:var(--gold);border:none;border-radius:50px;
  padding:12px 30px;font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:900;
  cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(107,63,26,.35);transition:all .2s;
}
.restart:active{transform:scale(.94);}
.credit{font-size:10px;color:rgba(107,63,26,.45);font-weight:700;}

/* confetti */
#cb{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:1000;overflow:hidden;}
.cf{position:absolute;width:9px;height:9px;animation:cf linear forwards;border-radius:2px;}
@keyframes cf{0%{transform:translateY(-10px) rotate(0);opacity:1}100%{transform:translateY(105vh) rotate(720deg);opacity:0}}

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   RESPONSIVE
═══════════════════════════════════════════ */
@media(max-height:580px){
  .drawing-area{max-height:170px;}
  .cover-title{font-size:34px;}
  .cover-mama{font-size:42px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="cb"></div>

<div class="book" id="book">

<!-- ═══════════════ P0 COVER ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page active" id="p0">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 15%, rgba(255,255,255,.5) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 75%, rgba(255,200,160,.6) 0%, transparent 50%);z-index:0;pointer-events:none;"></div>
  <div class="cover-wrap">
    <div class="cover-ribbon">📚 Libro Interactivo para Colorear</div>
    <div class="cover-mama">👩‍👦</div>
    <div class="cover-title">La Regla de los<br>10 Minutos</div>
    <div class="cover-animals-row">
      <span class="cov-a">🐰</span>
      <span class="cov-a">🐶</span>
      <span class="cov-a">🐿️</span>
      <span class="cov-a">🦊</span>
      <span class="cov-a">🐻</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-sub">Colorea · Aprende · Mamá descansa ☕</div>
    <div class="cover-promise">
      <strong>✨ El secreto que funciona:</strong> Mientras tu niño colorea a sus amigos animales, mamá tiene <strong>10 minutos de paz</strong> para recargar energía.
    </div>
    <div class="cover-pill">🎯 Para niños de 2 a 6 años</div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav">
    <button class="nbtn nbtn-back" disabled>←</button>
    <div class="pg-dots" id="d0"></div>
    <button class="nbtn nbtn-next" onclick="go(1)">Siguiente →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════ P1 CARTA MAMÁS ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page txt-page" id="p1">
  <div class="paper-texture"></div>
  <div class="txt-body">
    <div class="pg-label">💌 Carta para mamá</div>
    <div class="pg-h1">¿Por qué este libro<br><em>te va a cambiar el día?</em></div>
    <div class="body-p">Sabemos que criar es <strong>el trabajo más bonito y agotador</strong> del mundo. Cada día luchas con las mismas batallas…</div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">😩</div><div><div class="card-t">El problema que conoces bien</div><div class="card-s">Los niños no juegan solos más de 2 minutos y mamá nunca descansa de verdad.</div></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🎨</div><div><div class="card-t">La solución que funciona</div><div class="card-s">Colorear activa el foco infantil total. Un niño con lápices puede concentrarse 10–20 min.</div></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🧠</div><div><div class="card-t">El doble beneficio</div><div class="card-s">Mientras colorea aprende valores con sus amigos animales. ¡Sin que te des cuenta!</div></div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">☕</div><div><div class="card-t">Tu regalo: 10 minutos</div><div class="card-s">Esos 10 minutos de recarga te hacen más paciente, más presente, mejor mamá.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tip-box"><strong>💡 Así funciona:</strong> Siéntate con tu peque, abre una página de colorear, dale sus lápices y di: <em>"Colorea a Conejita mientras mamá descansa."</em> ¡Es magia real!</div>
  </div>
  <div class="nav">
    <button class="nbtn nbtn-back" onclick="go(-1)">←</button>
    <div class="pg-dots" id="d1"></div>
    <button class="nbtn nbtn-next" onclick="go(1)">Siguiente →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════ P2 ÍNDICE ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page txt-page" id="p2">
  <div class="paper-texture"></div>
  <div class="txt-body">
    <div class="pg-label">📋 Contenido</div>
    <div class="pg-h1">¿Qué vamos a<br><em>colorear hoy?</em></div>
